          <h2>The Meaning of "Stress"</h2>

          <div>
            <p class="mb-1">To be stressed means that:</p>

            <ul class="mb-8">
              <li>There is a heavy demand placed upon us, which needs a lot of physical and/or mental power to cope with. Such a demand is called a <strong>STRESSOR</strong>.</li>
              <li>We feel tension or a mismatch between the demand placed upon us and our own abilities and/or desire to meet that demand.</li>
            </ul>

